<subSubSection id="9A85652DFFD5FFE5B0ABFEF8E5CBFDCB" pageId="1" pageNumber="4" type="description">
<paragraph id="D22036A6FFD5FFE5B0ABFEF8E5CEFE6B" blockId="1.[170,1229,371,590]" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">
The diagnostic features of 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD5FFE5B25BFEF8E4B0FE08" authorityName="Banks" authorityYear="1940" box="[559,722,371,397]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Himalopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD5FFE5B25BFEF8E4B0FE08" box="[559,722,371,397]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">Himalopsyche</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
include: metascutellum with spiniferous warts; the venation is similar to that of 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD5FFE5B208FE18E56EFE28" authorityName="Pictet" authorityYear="1834" box="[636,780,403,429]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Rhyacophila" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD5FFE5B208FE18E56EFE28" box="[636,780,403,429]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">Rhyacophila</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
except forewing veins R and M curve backward so that R 
<subScript id="4E1B34E3FFD5FFE5B1F9FE4DE7F7FE51" attach="left" box="[397,405,454,468]" fontSize="6" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">4</subScript>
and R 
<subScript id="4E1B34E3FFD5FFE5B197FE4DE789FE53" attach="left" box="[483,491,454,470]" fontSize="6" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">5</subScript>
are on each side of the wing apex; the discoidal cell is open in both fore and hind wings; and the abdomen lacks ventral process.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D22036A6FFD5FFE5B0ABFE78E5CBFDCB" blockId="1.[170,1229,371,590]" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">
<bibRefCitation id="B60E4B57FFD5FFE5B0ABFE78E407FD8B" author="Schmid, F. &amp; Botosaneanu, L." box="[223,613,499,526]" pageId="1" pageNumber="4" pagination="123 - 176" refId="ref8079" refString="Schmid, F., Botosaneanu, L. Le genre Himalopsyche Banks (Trichoptera, Rhyacophilidae) // Annales de la Societe Entomologique de Quebec. - 1966. - 11. - P. 123 - 176." type="book chapter" year="1966">Schmid &amp; Botosaneanu (1966)</bibRefCitation>
divided 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD5FFE5B294FE78E5E1FD88" authorityName="Banks" authorityYear="1940" box="[736,899,499,525]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Himalopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD5FFE5B294FE78E5E1FD88" box="[736,899,499,525]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">Himalopsyche</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
into two distinct groups (
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD5FFE5B0C0FD9FE70CFDA8" baseAuthorityName="Ulmer" baseAuthorityYear="1927" box="[180,366,531,557]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Himalopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kuldschensis">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD5FFE5B0C0FD9FE70CFDA8" box="[180,366,531,557]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">H. kuldschensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group and 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD5FFE5B278FD9FE4FAFDA8" authorityName="Martynov. Original" authorityYear="1930" box="[524,664,531,557]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Rhyacophila" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tibetana">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD5FFE5B278FD9FE4FAFDA8" box="[524,664,531,557]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">H. tibetana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group) and five subgroups (
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD5FFE5B478FD9FE2A4FDA8" baseAuthorityName="Ulmer" baseAuthorityYear="1927" box="[1036,1222,531,557]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Himalopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kuldschensis">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD5FFE5B478FD9FE2A4FDA8" box="[1036,1222,531,557]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">H. kuldschensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD5FFE5B0DEFDBFE727FDC8" authorityName="Schmid" authorityYear="1963" box="[170,325,563,589]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Himalopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angnorbui">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD5FFE5B0DEFDBFE727FDC8" box="[170,325,563,589]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">H. angnorbui</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD5FFE5B127FDBFE7A0FDC8" authorityName="Banks" authorityYear="1940" box="[339,450,564,589]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Himalopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="navasi">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD5FFE5B127FDBFE7A0FDC8" box="[339,450,564,589]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">H. navasi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD5FFE5B1BBFDBFE431FDC8" authorityName="Martynov. Original" authorityYear="1930" box="[463,595,563,589]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Rhyacophila" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tibetana">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD5FFE5B1BBFDBFE431FDC8" box="[463,595,563,589]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">H. tibetana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="159F4D25FFD5FFE5B2F9FDBFE575FDC8" box="[653,791,563,589]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyacophilidae" genus="Himalopsyche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="anomala">
<emphasis id="E0EBEAB4FFD5FFE5B2F9FDBFE575FDC8" box="[653,791,563,589]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="4">H. anomala</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
subgroups).
</paragraph>
